1. /src/index.html this fille will produce the html file you wish to show

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>TestApp01</title>
  <base href="/">

  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="favicon.ico">
</head>
<body>
  // The app-root tag is grabing the html file that is nested within /src/app/app.component.html
  <app-root></app-root>
</body>
</html>


2. /src/style.css will produce gloabl css styling to all component files.



